Spring Security 2
- Using yml property structure
- Always have DTOs for your Models
- Created Password Encoder as a generalized method
- User Registration (Token Gen / Verification / Resend on Expire)
- Password Reset (Token Gen / Verification) Same as User Registration
    - Flow : In-General Scenario
        - User Send request for password reset
        - Mail is sent through a token which is maintained by DB
        - if valid then it shows the password reset form
        - New password details from the reset form are saved
- Password Change
    - Flow : In-General Scenario
        - User Send request for password change with old password + new password + email
        - verify old password for user by email
        - save new encoded password